rating_comment: The apartment is in a great location, easy accessible and there was a lot to do around. The host was incredible, took prompt action anytime we communicated for support. Overall, we are very satisfied staying at this place.

The Host is very helpful and kind person. He organised everything as we needed on demand. The Appartment is a nice and clean. The location is great and very convinence to move any where in the city. Overall we had a wonderful experience to stay in the Mr. Kawser's place. Wish them best of luck. Thank you.

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · November 2023,  · Stayed over a week
rating_comment: We thoroughly enjoyed our stay at this location. It offered tranquility, convenient access to various places, and provided an ideal setting for our family gathering. The caretakers were exceptionally helpful and always responsive to our needs.

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · June 2023,  · Stayed with kids
rating_comment: Mr. Kawser Hossain is a true gentleman. He has resolved all the problems I have encountered during my stay at his apartment. He is very kind, soft-spoken, and very prompt. He has called me almost every day to check if there is any issue that needs his attention. He has also sent out a maid to clean the floor and mop it. The apartment is in a prime location and highly maintained. A lot of activities can be done due to its proximity to the lake, convenience store, mosque, and most notably so many nearby restaurants to eat or the foods can be ordered from. I’d highly recommend his place to stay. Thank you.
